column5: Just wondering if anyone knows where I can get my hands on a map of Dogpaw lake, and possibly Caviar also? I've been going to Dogpaw for several years, and have been using an old hand-drawn map. thanks

Do you mean depth contour maps? I don't think they exist. I have seen maps of terrain from surveys that show elevations etc. but I haven't seen depth maps. Where do you stay? Are you primarily on Dogpaw or Caviar also?
I'm pretty much looking for any map I can find, depth contours or not, we mostly fish dogpaw, but last year I started fishing smallmouths on Caviar a little also.
I'm pretty much looking for any map I can find, depth contours or not, we mostly fish dogpaw, but last year I started fishing smallmouths on Caviar a little also.

On your way up, The Fisherman gas store in Int'l Falls has many paper maps. You'll have to search for it but I'm sure you'll find a map of the area. My friend bought one there years ago on my first trip up.
